== Months of Kinoe-Ushi == The twelfth month (December) of Gregorian calendar years ending in 2 or 7 (Heavenly Stems 壬 or 丁) corresponds to Kinoe-Ushi months. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|二十四節気|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Shōkan|ja|小寒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōkan|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|qq=}}) in traditional contexts.
== Days of Kinoe-Ushi == === Auspicious Dates === Days of Kinoe-Ushi are noted as intercalary days during the {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}} period. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
